high_descs: Turn left, enter a big room in front of you, keep going straight until there is an entrance to a room to your left, but turn right and walk to a dresser under a TV on the left side of the room that is closer to you.
Pick up a pan from the dresser.
Turn left, walk straight parallel to a kitchen sink and a countertop on your left, and stop by a fridge that is at the end in the upper left.
Place the pan inside the fridge, let it cool for a bit, and take it out.
Now go back and stop to face a countertop you were passing by before.
Place the pan on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled pan on the countertop.
